JoyRide is a leading homegrown superapp in the Philippines offering on-demand services in ride-hailing, delivery, and e-commerce. Operating 24/7, JoyRide covers cities across Metro Manila, Rizal, Bulacan, Cavite, Laguna, Baguio, Metro Cebu, and more!

Launched in 2019, JoyRide started as a motorcycle taxi service as an answer to the call of commuters for a safe and reliable transport alternative. Since then, JoyRide has served millions of bookings across the country and has successfully evolved into a superapp.

JoyRide’s mission has always been to empower its growing networks of customers, driver-partners, and merchant partners by providing convenient and accessible solutions through a scalable multi-service technology platform. Today, JoyRide continues to grow its list of product offerings and is committed to providing quality value-for-money services to everyone and anyone who needs it.

Ride-hailing

• JoyRide Car (New!)
Enjoy comfortable and affordable rides to your destination using a private car! 

• JoyRide MC Taxi
Beat the traffic on a motorcycle taxi! Have our Kasundo Bikers bring you safely and swiftly to your destination.

• JoyRide Taxicle
Get around fast and easy with our tricycle service option! Available in select cities. 

Delivery

• JoyRide Delivery
Express motorcycle deliveries for those on the go! Send documents, parcels, food, and more! 

• JoyRide Pabili
Run your errands with us! Have our Kasundo Bikers buy items for you from restaurants, groceries, drugstores, and more!

• Happy Move
Same-day courier delivery service via motorcycles, cars, vans, and trucks! With round-trip, multi-stop, and scheduling features! 

E-commerce

• JR Mall
Online marketplace for food, groceries, lifestyle, and essential items! Order from a wide selection of restaurants, marts, & shops and have them delivered to your doorstep instantly or at a scheduled time! 

• Buy Load
No need to look elsewhere! You can now purchase mobile prepaid load and load packages for you and your friends.

CYCLY is a technology-driven mobility platform that enables Integrated Urban Mobility across public and private modes of transport. Using Micro Mobility Vehicles (MMVs) through a user-friendly mobile app, CYCLY enables first and last-mile connectivity that is seamless, shared, and sustainable. CYCLY Move is a smart lock enabled bicycle which effectively solves the first mile, last mile, and short distance commute challenges. Take a Move to run errands, travel short distances or use it as a fitness friend. Pedal the change for a clean and green environment!

CYCLY’s mission is to make urban mobility in Qatar seamless, shareable, and sustainable. What started off as an initiative to reduce traffic congestion and pollution
in Qatar, is now redefining urban mobility across the country. We are driven by three guiding principles of urban mobility Accessibility, Availability, and Affordability.
We are empowering residents in Qatar to create a paradigm shift in the mobility industry, by making the urban commute more efficient and Eco-friendlier.
